item.title: Finding My Way.
item.description: Despite the last post, I’m still struggling to find that rhythm. I realized I’m holding myself back significantly in multiple ways. I haven’t worked on my confidence in any major way, and that’s slowing me. Adding to that is my ability to make excuses for not starting anything. The only way to get better is to put in consistent work. Whether I want to make music, write, skate, or improve my mental health â€” I have to stick to it.
